label: MedicalProcedureType
comment: An enumeration that describes different types of medical procedures.

enumerationMembers.label: NoninvasiveProcedure
enumerationMembers.comment: A type of medical procedure that involves noninvasive techniques.

enumerationMembers.label: PercutaneousProcedure
enumerationMembers.comment: A type of medical procedure that involves percutaneous techniques, where access to organs or tissue is achieved via needle-puncture of the skin. For example, catheter-based procedures like stent delivery.
